  "text": "Nowadays new insights into BD immunopathogenesis provide novel therapeutic approaches. Clinical and laboratory observations proved the important role of TNF-α. During the last 10 years, TNF-α antagonist drugs such as infliximab, adalimumab and etanercept have been successfully used by patients with BD [CITATION_1] .",
